### Playlists
<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR001167-0/playlist.png"><br>

**This feature is currently in preview**
Create named collections of apps for repeatable batch installations. Supports export/import with feed remapping.

| Name | Description | Page Action | Grid Action |
|------|-------------|:-----------:|:-----------:|
| Copy | Duplicate the selected playlist | ✅ | ❌ |
| Export | Export playlists as a `.zip` file | ✅ | ❌ |
| Import | Import playlists from a `.zip` file with feed remapping | ✅ | ❌ |


### Playlist Apps
<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR001167-0/playlistapps.png"><br>

View and manage apps assigned to a playlist. Missing feeds are highlighted in red for easy identification.

| Name | Description | Page Action | Grid Action |
|------|-------------|:-----------:|:-----------:|
| Remove Selected | Remove the selected app from the playlist | ✅ | ❌ |
| Change Feed | Change the feed assignment for the selected app | ✅ | ❌ |
| Repair Feeds | Remap or remove apps pointing to feeds that no longer exist | ✅ | ❌ |
